      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4074">
            <h1 id="chief-operating-officer">Chief Operating Officer</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Board members give corporate leadership to the <abbr title="Foreign & Commonwealth Office">FCO</abbr> by ensuring that the department meets the foreign policy priorities, Public Service Agreements targets and service delivery targets set by ministers. The Chief Operating Officer is responsible for the running of the <abbr title="Foreign & Commonwealth Office">FCO</abbr> as an organisation and has the following areas of responsibility:</p>

<ul>
  <li>human resources</li>
  <li>finance</li>
  <li>estates</li>
  <li>security</li>
  <li>IT</li>
  <li>corporate services</li>
  <li>protocol</li>
</ul>

</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/foreign-commonwealth-office">Foreign & Commonwealth Office</a>
</p>

